<!-- views/create-level.hbs -->
<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #dee2e6; border-radius: 6px; padding: 20px;">
  <h2 style="color: #007bff; border-bottom: 2px solid #007bff; padding-bottom: 8px;">New Approval Level Created</h2>

  <p>Hello,</p>

  <p>A new approval level has been successfully created in the system. Below are the details:</p>

  <table cellpadding="8" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse; background: #f8f9fa; border: 1px solid #dee2e6; margin-top: 10px;">
    <tr>
      <td width="30%" style="border: 1px solid #dee2e6;"><strong>Level Name</strong></td>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #dee2e6;">{{levelName}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #dee2e6;"><strong>Description</strong></td>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #dee2e6;">{{description}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #dee2e6;"><strong>Status</strong></td>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #dee2e6;">{{status}}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <p style="margin-top: 15px;">
    You can now manage or assign actions for this approval level from the administration panel.
  </p>

  <br/>

  <p style="font-size: 0.95em; color: #343a40;">
    Regards,<br/>
    <strong>System Administrator</strong><br/>
    <span style="color: #007bff;">Mwalimu Commercial Bank PLC</span><br/>
    <small>Automated System Notification</small>
  </p>

  <div style="border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6; margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 10px; text-align: center; color: #6c757d; font-size: 0.85em;">
    This is an automated message — please do not reply.<br/>
    © {{year}} Mwalimu Commercial Bank PLC. All rights reserved.
  </div>
</div>
